nodes.text: Keenos was an entertainer residing in Ord Mynock Freeport. He entertained crowds in the Atrium by juggling clubs lit on fire while reciting stanzas of the poem "The Dread Pirate Kragg." Keenos would often pass around a hat after his performances, asking for donations to the Old Spacers' Entertainment Hospice which consisted mostly of himself. A Rebel sympathizer, Keenos would help Alliance agents whenever possible.
